                           <desc>: Transaction note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#158va">158va</locus>: ሐምሌ᎓ ፲፩ ቀን᎓ ፵፯ ዓምሕ[ረ]ት᎓ ይኸውና᎓
